                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8559" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1308</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1547 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值重塑：HT公司与LD公司的人力外包年度谈判 (A)(B)(C)</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value Reshaping: Annual Human Resource Outsourcing Negotiation between HT Company and LD Company(A)(B)(C)</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙晓枫，李玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">和光舒卷（广东）数字科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力外包谈判；整合型谈判；谈判替代方案（BATNA）；决策认知偏差；价值创造；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Human Resource Outsourcing Negotiation; Integrative Negotiation; Best Alternative to a Negotiated Agreement (BATNA); Decision-Making Cognitive Bias; Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例详细描述探讨了HT人力外包有限公司（以下简称“HT公司”）与LD科技公司（以下简称“LD公司”）之间的年度人力外包服务价格谈判过程。HT公司面临LD公司提出的年度降价要求，经过对LD公司的质疑和威胁作出应对，调整“价值分配”为“价值创造”的谈判策略，最终与LD公司达成了协议。
本案例描述的谈判具备典型整合型谈判的特征和演进过程，案例中包含了谈判准备的关键要素、分歧解决的三种方式、谈判者的系统性决策认知偏差、通过认别差异创造价值等。通过此案例讨论，有助于理解谈判的本质和谈判过程中应遵循的重要原则，掌握分歧解决方式和价值创造的方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study provides a detailed account of the annual human resource outsourcing service price negotiation process between HT Human Resources Outsourcing Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;HT Company&quot;) and LD Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;LD Company&quot;). Faced with LD Company&#39;s annual price reduction demand, HT Company responded to LD&#39;s questioning and threats by adjusting its negotiation strategy from &quot;value distribution&quot; to &quot;value creation,&quot; ultimately reaching an agreement with LD Company. The negotiation described in this case exhibits typical characteristics and the evolutionary process of an integrative negotiation. The case includes key elements of negotiation preparation, three ways to resolve disagreements, systematic decision-making cognitive biases of negotiators, and creating value by recognizing differences. Discussion of this case helps to understand the essence of negotiation and the important principles to follow during the negotiation process, as well as methods for resolving disagreements and creating value.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商务谈判》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谈判的本质、类型与基本策略选择；谈判准备的四个关键点；谈判者三种关键性和系统性的决策认知偏差；解决分歧的三种方式；价值创造的原则和利用差异进行交易设计。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
